2&amp;amp;text=Is%20Your%20Website%20Ready%20For%202012%3F%20%20&quot; class=&quot;social-share-twitter&quot; title=&quot;Twitter&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Twitter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
