<item>
 <title>Best Social Media Blogs </title>
 <link>https://www.verdadesign.com/blog/best-social-media-blogs</link>
 <description>
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
	  
          &lt;div class=&quot;dnd-atom-wrapper type-image context-sdl_editor_representation&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;dnd-drop-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- scald=182:sdl_editor_representation {&quot;option&quot;:&quot;{\u201clink\u201d:\u201d\u201c}&quot;} --&gt;&lt;div class=&#039;image&#039;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.verdadesign.com/assets/thumbnails/image/social-media-sharing.jpg&quot; width=&quot;1000&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;social-media-sharing.jpg&quot; title=&quot;social-media-sharing.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- END scald=182 --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following are social media blogs that I find interesting and check regularly. Some are well known and others are fairly new but have great content and potential. These are listed in no particular order.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.socialmediaexplorer.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;social media&quot;&gt;Social Media Explorer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.socialmediaexplorer.com/about/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;jason falls&quot;&gt;Jason Falls&lt;/a&gt; is co-founder and president of Social Media Club Louisville and writes regularly for Social Media Explorer. This blog is great to check out for social media savvy marketers for the latest news and insights in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/#!/jasonfalls&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;jason falls twitter&quot;&gt;Follow Jason Falls On Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://plus.google.com/102864603075591269997&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;jason falls twitter&quot;&gt;Follow Jason Falls on Google Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://sparkerstrategy.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;social media winnipeg&quot;&gt;Sparker Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://sparkerstrategy.ca/about-us/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;susie parker&quot;&gt;Susie Parker&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=&quot;http://sparkerstrategy.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;susie parker&quot;&gt;Sparker Strategy Group&lt;/a&gt; blogs often about social media, marketing, and &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;PR&lt;/span&gt;. She is a local &lt;a href=&quot;http://sparkerstrategy.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;social media winnipeg&quot;&gt;social media expert in Winnipeg&lt;/a&gt;, Manitoba and brings an interesting point of view and personality to each post. Her posts are well composed and easy to understand for people just beginning to get interested in social media as well as social media experts. She brings a fresh point of view to the table.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/#!/susie_parker&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Twitter Susie Parker&quot;&gt;Follow Susie Parker On Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://plus.google.com/110807443898756699281/posts&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;social media&quot;&gt;Follow Susie Parker On Google Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://womengrowbusiness.com/&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;women grow business&quot;&gt;Women Grow Business&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a great &lt;a href=&quot;social%20media&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;social media blog&quot;&gt;social media blog&lt;/a&gt; written by women for anyone interested in the subject or anyone growing their business in general. The blog covers a wide array of social media, &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;PR&lt;/span&gt;, and marketing topics. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chrisbrogan.com/&quot; style=&quot;border-style: initial; border-color: initial;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;chris brogan blog&quot;&gt;Chris Brogan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chrisbrogan.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;chris brogan blog&quot;&gt;Chris Brogan&lt;/a&gt; has a passion for social media and it shows by his frequently well thought out posts on the subject. He has a great way of merging business and the new form of communication that is social media to help it make sense to companies and individuals alike.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/#!/chrisbrogan&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;chris brogan on twitter&quot;&gt;Follow Chris Brogan On Twitter &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://plus.google.com/118320665823821681206/posts&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;google plus&quot;&gt;Follow Chris Brogan On Google Plus &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mashable.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;mashable&quot;&gt;Mashable&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We had to mention &lt;a href=&quot;http://mashable.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;mashable&quot;&gt;Mashable&lt;/a&gt;. I end up checking out this site a couple of times a day for the latest in social media trends and breaking stories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/#!/mashable&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Twitter Mashable&quot;&gt;Follow Mashable On Twitter &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://plus.google.com/101849747879612982297/posts&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;google plus&quot;&gt;Follow Mashable On Google Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.hubspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;hub spot&quot;&gt;Hub Spot Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.hubspot.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;hub spot&quot;&gt;Hub Spot&lt;/a&gt; has a very complete blog covering a wide variety of topics pertaining to modern day marketing from social media platforms to marketing tips and how to improve your business online. They cover most of the large social networks such as Linkedin, Twitter, and Facebook with tips on how to achieve marketing goals and engage through social media.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/#!/hubspot&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Twitter&quot;&gt;Follow Hub Spot On Twitter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What’s your favorite social media blog? Please feel free to comment.&lt;/p&gt;
    
&lt;/div&gt;

